    <entry>
      <title>Github+Picgo搭建图床</title>
      <link href="2021/06/04/jsDelivr-Github-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>2021/06/04/jsDelivr-Github-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1><a href="#github" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="github">Github</span></h1><h2><a href="#zhu-ce-zhang-hu" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="zhu-ce-zhang-hu">注册账户</span></h2><p>在<a href="https://github.com/">github</a>首页注册自己的github账户</p><h2><a href="#chuang-jian-cang-ku" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="chuang-jian-cang-ku">创建仓库</span></h2><p>点击右上角的 “+”，选择 New repositories<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604223002.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604221849.png"></p><h2><a href="#chuang-jian-token" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="chuang-jian-token">创建token</span></h2><p>此时仓库已经建立，点击右上角头像，在点击setting进入设置；<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604223401.png"><br>在左侧页面最下找到 Developer settings，点击进入；<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604223456.png"><br>创建token<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604223620.png"><br>填写description（随心填），勾选复选框 repo ，接着到页面底部 Generate token 就完成了<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604223803.png"><br>然后复制生成一串字符 token，这个 token 只出现一次，所以要保存一下。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/PIC/img/20210604225159.png"></p><h1><a href="#picgo" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="picgo">Picgo</span></h1>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Hexo </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
