    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Aplayer教程</title>
      <link href="2021/05/30/Aplayer%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>2021/05/30/Aplayer%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p><a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer/blob/master/docs/README-zh_cn.md">项目地址</a></p><div class="note info modern"><p>感谢开源！！让我们用上了这么好的插件！</p></div><h1><a href="#chuang-jian-du-li-ye-mian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="chuang-jian-du-li-ye-mian">创建独立页面</span></h1><h2><a href="#ye-mian-chuang-jian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="ye-mian-chuang-jian">页面创建</span></h2><p>在终端输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n page playlist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><a href="#xiu-gai-ye-mian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="xiu-gai-ye-mian">修改页面</span></h2><p>在博客目录/Hexo/source会出现一个playlist文件夹，修改其中的index.md文件。如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 歌单</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-02-21 16:14:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;playlist&quot;`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><a href="#xiu-gai-zhu-ti-wen-jian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="xiu-gai-zhu-ti-wen-jian">修改主题文件</span></h2><p>打开主题的 _config.yml文件，在menu下新建一个名为playlist的类（注意这里使用的图标是图标库中的图标，网址为 <a href="https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/</a> 。）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  主页: / || fas fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  文章||far fa-file-alt:</span><br><span class="line">    标签: /tags/ || fas fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">    分类: /categories/ || fas fa-folder-open</span><br><span class="line">    时间轴: /archives/ || fas fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">    音乐: /playlist/ || fas fa-music</span><br><span class="line">  友链: /link/ || fas fa-link</span><br><span class="line">  关于: /about/ || fas fa-heart</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><a href="#xiu-gai-ye-mian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="xiu-gai-ye-mian">修改页面</span></h2><p>打开/Hexo/source/playlist/index.md，添加如下内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 音乐</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-02-21 16:14:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;playlist&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1><a href="#an-zhuang-amp-pei-zhi" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="an-zhuang-amp-pei-zhi">安装&amp;配置</span></h1><h2><a href="#an-zhuang-cha-jian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="an-zhuang-cha-jian">安装插件</span></h2><p>hexo-tag-aplayer是Aplayer在Hexo上面的音乐插件。在终端执行以下内容：(参考<a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer/blob/master/docs/README-zh_cn.md">官方文档</a>)</p>   <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-tag-aplayer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><a href="#xiu-gai-pei-zhi-wen-jian" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="xiu-gai-pei-zhi-wen-jian">修改配置文件</span></h2><p>最新版的 hexo-tag-aplayer 已经支持了MetingJS的使用，可以直接解析网络平台的歌曲如<mark class="hl-label green">QQ音乐</mark> 、<mark class="hl-label red">网易云音乐</mark> 、<mark class="hl-label orange">虾米</mark> 、<mark class="hl-label blue">酷狗</mark> 、<mark class="hl-label blue">百度</mark> 等平台，首先要在站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中开启meting模式，添加以下代码在配置文件的最后：</p>   <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aplayer:</span><br><span class="line">  meting: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><a href="#she-zhi-ge-dan" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="she-zhi-ge-dan">设置歌单</span></h2><p>配置歌单。例如复制歌单的链接，然后复制歌单的id，例如<code>https://music.163.com/#/playlist?id=395276323</code>这个歌单的id就是395276323，公司名可以是<code>netease</code>, <code>tencent</code>, <code>kugou</code>, <code>xiami</code>, <code>baidu</code>，下面给出一个例子，打开 /Hexo/source/playlist/<a href="https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=http://index.md">index.md</a>文件，输入：(其他详细配置参数请参照<a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer/blob/master/docs/README-zh_cn.md">Github项目</a>)</p>   <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% meting &quot;2653805335&quot; &quot;netease&quot; &quot;playlist&quot; &quot;theme:#FF4081&quot; &quot;mode:circulation&quot; &quot;mutex:true&quot; &quot;listmaxheight:340px&quot; &quot;preload:auto&quot; &quot;autoplay&quot; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>   效果如下图：</p><p><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/06/04/2YhJOS.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
